Here telegram bot using chat gpt API.


Example of bot structure with MVC:
bot/
    __init__.py
    config.py
    controller/
        __init__.py
        base_controller.py
        message_controller.py
    model/
        __init__.py
        base_model.py
        message_model.py
    view/
        __init__.py
        base_view.py
        message_view.py
